585
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:33,467
Yes.

586
00:34:34,093 --> 00:34:36,846
I'll make sure that happens, Kaya.

587
00:34:41,601 --> 00:34:43,978
SUWON DISTRICT COURT,
CRIMINAL PANEL DIVISION

588
00:34:44,061 --> 00:34:47,106
In this case,
the father-in-law sexually assaulted

589
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:51,068
his lonely daughter-in-law,
who had come from a distant land.

590
00:34:51,152 --> 00:34:54,197
Under Article 5, Paragraph 1
of the Act on Special Cases

591
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,407
Concerning the Punishment
of Sexual Crimes,

592
00:34:57,033 --> 00:34:59,869
it is a felony with a fixed term
of over seven years in prison,

593
00:35:00,411 --> 00:35:04,248
and the defendant
has to be held fully accountable.

594
00:35:04,874 --> 00:35:08,586
The Court cannot dare to imagine

595
00:35:09,545 --> 00:35:14,342
the pain the victim is enduring
because of this.

596
00:35:15,843 --> 00:35:18,638
-Therefore…
-Therefore…

597
00:35:18,721 --> 00:35:20,264
-However…
-What?

598
00:35:20,348 --> 00:35:21,557
…the defendant is of old age,

599
00:35:22,141 --> 00:35:26,646
and hundreds of local residents
have appealed for clemency.

600
00:35:26,729 --> 00:35:30,191
Moreover, he is a first-time offender
without any criminal history.

601
00:35:30,274 --> 00:35:33,194
No way. He isn't building up
to a suspended sentence, is he?

602
00:35:33,277 --> 00:35:36,614
The statutory penalty is seven years.
A reduction is three years and six months.

603
00:35:36,697 --> 00:35:40,159
A suspended sentence is possible
for up to three years. It won't happen.

604
00:35:40,243 --> 00:35:42,787
Meanwhile, many residents testified

605
00:35:42,870 --> 00:35:47,041
and criticized how the victim
typically dressed and behaved.

606
00:35:47,124 --> 00:35:51,045
Considering the annulment of her marriage

607
00:35:51,754 --> 00:35:54,382
due to the victim's premarital childbirth
and fraudulent act,

608
00:35:55,007 --> 00:35:59,011
these testimonies cannot be taken lightly.

609
00:35:59,095 --> 00:36:02,848
At the time of the incident,
the defendant was heavily intoxicated,

610
00:36:02,932 --> 00:36:05,268
and as a result,
he lacked the capacity for judgment

611
00:36:05,351 --> 00:36:08,020
or the ability to make decisions.

612
00:36:08,104 --> 00:36:12,692
With diminished mental capacity
as the first mitigating factor

613
00:36:12,775 --> 00:36:15,695
and the various aforementioned facts
as the second,

614
00:36:15,778 --> 00:36:19,573
the Court renders the following judgment
mitigated at its discretion

615
00:36:19,657 --> 00:36:21,742
within the applicable sentencing range.

616
00:36:21,826 --> 00:36:24,996
Double mitigation? No way.

617
00:36:25,538 --> 00:36:28,040
The defendant is sentenced
to three years in prison.

618
00:36:28,833 --> 00:36:31,294
However, this sentence

619
00:36:31,377 --> 00:36:34,380
will be suspended for five years
from the date of this ruling.

620
00:36:34,463 --> 00:36:36,382
-What the…
-Order in the court.

621
00:36:38,175 --> 00:36:40,219
To hold the defendant fully accountable,

622
00:36:40,303 --> 00:36:42,388
the Court imposes
200 hours of community service

623
00:36:42,888 --> 00:36:46,851
and 80 hours
of sexual violence treatment courses.

624
00:36:47,476 --> 00:36:50,021
This concludes the Court's ruling.

625
00:36:51,939 --> 00:36:53,524
All rise.

626
00:37:08,956 --> 00:37:10,499
Thank you, Mr. Woo.

627
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:16,213
But aren't those too many hours
for community service?

628
00:37:16,297 --> 00:37:18,049
Geez, Mr. Cho.

629
00:37:18,132 --> 00:37:21,052
You have always
provided service for the community.

630
00:37:21,552 --> 00:37:23,054
You can do a little more.

631
00:37:23,137 --> 00:37:24,680
Okay. Have a good day.

632
00:37:24,764 --> 00:37:26,265
All right. Goodbye.

633
00:37:28,601 --> 00:37:32,229
After sitting on the judge's bench
for so long, I'd forgotten…

634
